quran[10{c,v,t}:
30,51,aur agar hum aik aisi howa bhaij den jis ke assar se woh apni khaiti ko zard payen to woh kufar karte reh jatay hain
30,52,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum mُrdon ko nahi suna satke, nah unn behroon ko apni pukaar suna satke ho jo peeth phairay bhage chalay ja rahay hon"
30,53,aur nah tum andhon ko un ki gumraahi se nikaal kar raah e raast dikha satke ho tum to sirf unhi ko suna satke ho jo hamari ayaat par imaan laatay aur sar-e tasleem khham kar dete hain
30,54,"Allah hi to hai jis ne zeaf ki haalat mein tumhari paidaiesh ki ibtida ki, phir is zeaf ke baad tumhe qowat bakhsh, phir is qowat ke baad tumhe zaeef aur boorha kar diya woh jo kuch chahta hai peda karta hai aur woh sab kuch jan-nay wala, har cheez par qudrat rakhnay wala hai"
30,55,"aur jab woh saa-at barpaa ho gi to mujrim kasmain kha kha kar kahin ge ke hum aik gharri bhar se ziyada nahi thire hain, isi terhan woh duniya ki zindagi mein dhoka khaya karte thay"
30,56,"magar jo ilm aur imaan se behra mand kiye gay thay woh kahin ge ke khuda ke noshte mein to tum rozِ hashar taq parre rahay ho, so yeh wohi rozِ hashar hai, lekin tum jantay nah thay"
30,57,pas woh din ho ga jis mein zaalmon ko un ki moazrat koi naffa nah day gi aur nah un se maffi mangnay ke liye kaha jaye ga
30,58,"hum ne iss quran mein logon ko terhan terhan se samjhaya hai tum khuwa koi nishani le aao, jin logon ne maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai woh yahi kahin ge ke tum baatil par ho"
30,59,iss terhan thp_h laga deta hai Allah unn logon ke dilon par jo be ilm hain
30,60,"pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) sabr karo, yaqeenan Allah ka wada sacha hai, aur hargiz halka nah payen tum ko woh log jo yaqeen nahi laatay"
